The Managing Director of Airtel Nigeria Limited, Mr. Segun Ogunsanya, has commended the Executive Vice Chairman of the Nigerian Communications Commission, Prof. Umar Garba Danbatta, over what he described as the agency’s tough actions against the menace of call-masking and refilling in the telecommunication industry. Ogunsanya spoke when he accompanied Raghunath Mandava, Airtel’s Executive Director, Africa, and other top officials of the firm to a meeting with the NCC boss at the just concluded 2018 GSMA World Mobile Congress in Barcelona, Spain, a statement by NCC said yesterday.